{"tid":1191490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得應該要整個香港人 英靈殿 ???","createTime":"2019-06-08T03:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T04:13:43.000Z","uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2131525e5c229fa006e7857ebecf5453ada5149","tid":1191490,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"突然諗返起其實有好多人係為左香港付出好多，包括事業/生活同成個人生，但件事過左之後就無咩人仲會記得佢地既名，例子好似下面呢D...<br />\n<br />\n佔中無間道督察判囚27月<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171212/00176_010.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171212%2F00176_010.html&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8zizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=e984f8a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171212/00176_010.html</a><br />\n警務督察於佔領行動期間做「無間道」，從警方內聯網取得兩名「不斷挑釁市民」的警員資料後在網上公開。警方上門拘捕他時，更在其電腦和外置硬碟內，發現逾二百七十項兒童色情片段及照片。<br />\n<br />\n「美國隊長」容偉業、袁智駒判囚3年<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6275429/article-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E6%A1%88-%E3%80%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%8A%E9%95%B7%E3%80%8D%E5%AE%B9%E5%81%89%E6%A5%AD%E3%80%81%E8%A2%81%E6%99%BA%E9%A7%92%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6275429%2Farticle-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E3%2580%2581%25E8%25A2%2581%25E6%2599%25BA%25E9%25A7%2592%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A3%2F&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8zizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=f156040a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6275429/article-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E6%A1%88-%E3%80%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%8A%E9%95%B7%E3%80%8D%E5%AE%B9%E5%81%89%E6%A5%AD%E3%80%81%E8%A2%81%E6%99%BA%E9%A7%92%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A3/</a><br />\n<br />\n以上既兩位只係呢一大堆無咩英雄既其中一部份，<br />\n政府高官一邊賣港一邊拎緊幾十萬月薪，<br />\n而佢地為左香港付出成個人生但香港人可以比返D咩佢地? <br />\n政府係佔中過後靜靜雞拉左好多人，佢地比人拉左經歷左D咩無人知<br />\n但我真心希望香港人唔好忘記呢D無名英雄..<br />\n佢地每一個人都值得載入香港歷史英雄名冊，<br />\n有冇人有同感???"},{"pid":"79b3ab2eaa428ad054f6fda9505b5501bcd42dd4","tid":1191490,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef712df3e0eac6ed4d2bd3703bfd315efd8c83d9","tid":1191490,"uid":58821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"英乜撚殿，打少啲機啦。<br />\n就算比你整到，過左一排之後又會有咩人仲會記得英靈殿"}]}